# Stray compiled output: the src tree is all TypeScript. The old build ran
# `tsc -b` (no noEmit), which emitted .js next to every .tsx; the build now
# uses `tsgo --noEmit` so this shouldn't recur, but guard against it.
/src/**/*.js
/src/**/*.js.map
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
